room_title: Escape room "The Condo" by Escape Games AZ in Phoenix
room_address: 12 N. Center Street, Suite 200 Mesa, AZ 85201
room_description: Your cousins are looking to steal their mom's inheritance and even placed her in a retirement home to get rid of her faster. She's desperate to save her most prized possession, so she came to you, her favorite nieces and nephews. Help her retrieve the secret stash, and the inheritance is yours!
